PrecisAppointment of DAN QUIGLEY, of Victoria, British Columbia, as a full-time member of the Public Service Staff Relations Board to hold office during good behaviour for a period of two years; and order that DAN QUIGLEY shall be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act, effective November 19, 2001.
